item.title: Prayer bpn6113 in Chamorro
item.description: ##HINEMLO’ *HEALING I Na’an-Mu i hinemlo’-hu, O Yu’os-hu, ya i hi- nasso-ku put Hagu i remediu-hu. I hinihot giya Hagu ninangga-ku, ya i guinaiya para Hagu i ga’chong-hu. I mina’ase’-Mu giya guahu i hinem- lo’-hu yan alibiu-hu parehu guini na tano’ yan manmamamaila’ na tano! Hagu, sen magahet, i Todu Miguinaha, i Todu-Gaitiningo’, i Todu- Tomtom. Thy name is my healing, O my God, and remembrance of Thee is my remedy.
